A plugin for Pidgin
Pidgin Embedded Video is a GTK plugin for the popular instant messaging client \
Pidgin. This plugin provides you an easy way to watch videos from popular \
websites (CollegeHumor, Dailymotion, Google Video, Metacafe, MySpace Video, \
Trilulilu, Vimeo, Xfire, Yahoo! Video and Youtube) directly into the \
conversation. Share links and enjoy!
